CustomField.description:
The field which provides the Merge Rule Secondary Priority. If set to a blank value, a Merge Rule Field record should be added with a matching data type and flagged with Is Secondary Priority?.
E.g. Merge Rule Field: Address Last Updated, Is Secondary Priority?=TRUE.
